title: Surya
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Indian, Buffet, Beer/Wine, Nepalese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Menu includes a large variety of vegetarian suitable dishes: appetizers as well as main entrees. Vegans to ask about dairy use. Nice atmosphere with paintings and luxe facilities; the no-touch bathroom is popular with people who like hygiene. Centrally located in Amsterdam with Wi-Fi internet.
